SISHUBILE isimo eKatlehong eGoli izakhamizi zishaqa impahla enxanxatheleni yezitolo iSontoga ngoLwesibili ebusuku. Kusolakala ukuthi lezi zakhamizi ziqale zavala imigwaqo ukwenzela ukuthi izimoto zamaphoyisa zingakwazi ukungena zabe sezinikela eSontoga Mall, zagqekeza zatapa impahla.Â Okhulumela amaPhoyisa eGauteng uLieutenant-Colonel Lungelo Dlamini uthe, izakhamizi zibeke amatshe nokunye emgwaqweni ukuze zivimbele amaphoyisa phakathi kwamabili. UDlamini uthe, amaphoyisa abebizelwe endaweni yesigameko athole umgwaqo oholela kule ndawo ebekutatshwa kuyona impahla uvinjiwe.       